Trevor Noah has thanked fans for their continued support after The Daily Show walked away with 3 Emmy nominations. The comedian, who is in Russia for the Soccer World Cup, posted a picture of himself on Instagram, captioning it: “Wow, I visited Russia for 3 days and now The Daily Show is nominated for 3 Emmys. Next time I should stay for a week and then run for president. To all the people who voted for us and to all who watch our show I could not be more grateful.”.  Wow, I visited Russia for 3 days and now The Daily Show is nominated for 3 Emmys. Next time I should stay for a week and then run for president ?? To all the people who voted for us and to all who watch our show I could not be more grateful. Spasibo ???? #Emmys A post shared by  Trevor Noah (@trevornoah) on Jul 12, 2018 at 2:47pm PDT 